SUMMARY:Public Defense - Jérome Eertmans
URL:https://eertmans.be/posts/public-defense/
DESCRIPTION:(English below)\n\nJe suis heureux de vous inviter à la soutenance publique de ma thèse le lundi 6 juillet\, ainsi qu'à l'apéro et au repas qui suivront. Le lieu exact reste à préciser\, mais l'événement se tiendra dans un auditoire à Louvain-la-Neuve. Pour ceux en ligne\, cela se fera sur Teams (lien ci-dessous).\n\nLa présentation\, qui se fera en français\, commencera à 16 h 30 et devrait se terminer vers 18 h 30 au plus tard. Si vous ne pouvez pas assister à la présentation\, mais que vous souhaitez tout de même venir au drink ou au repas\, n'hésitez pas !\n\nPour des questions d'organisation\, pouvez-vous remplir ce formulaire ? \nhttps://forms.gle/rrtL3CEds8ARPf67A\n\n---\n\nI am pleased to invite you to the public defense of my dissertation on Monday\, July 6\, as well as to the drink and dinner that will follow. The exact location is still to be determined\, but the event will take place in a lecture hall in Louvain-la-Neuve.\nFor those joining online\, the meeting will take place on Teams (link below).\n\nThe presentation\, which will be in French\, will begin at 4:30 p.m. and is expected to end by 6:30 p.m. at the latest. If you are unable to attend the presentation but would still like to join us for drinks or dinner\, please feel free to come!\n\nFor organizational purposes\, could you please fill out this form? https://forms.gle/rrtL3CEds8ARPf67A\n\n---\n\nTeams: https://teams.microsoft.com/meet/3594970697800?p=FqJt4Q4BC3pMbScJ8s
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<!doctype html><html><body><em>English below</em>\n<br> Je suis heureux de vous inviter &agrave\; la soutenance publique de ma th&egrave\;se le lundi 6 juillet\, ainsi qu&apos\;&agrave\; l&apos\;ap&eacute\;ro et au repas qui suivront. Le lieu exact reste &agrave\; pr&eacute\;ciser\, mais l&apos\;&eacute\;v&eacute\;nement se tiendra dans un auditoire &agrave\; Louvain-la-Neuve. Pour ceux en ligne\, cela se fera sur Teams (lien ci-dessous). <br> La pr&eacute\;sentation\, qui se fera en fran&ccedil\;ais\, commencera &agrave\; 16 h 30 et devrait se terminer vers 18 h 30 au plus tard. Si vous ne pouvez pas assister &agrave\; la pr&eacute\;sentation\, mais que vous souhaitez tout de m&ecirc\;me venir au drink ou au repas\, n&apos\;h&eacute\;sitez pas ! <br> Pour des questions d&apos\;organisation\, pouvez-vous remplir ce formulaire ? <a href="https://forms.gle/rrtL3CEds8ARPf67A" target="_blank" id="OWAcedbcfd3-e97c-e062-32f1-a3d13242e88d" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://forms.gle/rrtL3CEds8ARPf67A</a>\n<br>\n<em>I am pleased to invite you to the public defense of my dissertation on Monday\, July 6\, as well as to the drink and dinner that will follow. The exact location is still to be determined\, but the event will take place in a lecture hall in Louvain-la-Neuve. For those joining online\, the meeting will take place on Teams (link below).</em>\n<br>\n<em>The presentation\, which will be in French\, will begin at 4:30 p.m. and is expected to end by 6:30 p.m. at the latest. If you are unable to attend the presentation but would still like to join us for drinks or dinner\, please feel free to come!</em>\n<br>\n<em>For organizational purposes\, could you please fill out this form?&nbsp\;</em><a href="https://forms.gle/rrtL3CEds8ARPf67A" target="_blank" id="OWAdfbdce13-e470-1ced-3d3f-c47701dc0897" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://forms.gle/rrtL3CEds8ARPf67A</a>\n<br> ________________________________________________________________________________ <br> R&eacute\;union Microsoft Teams <div><span>Rejoindre :&nbsp\;</span> <span><a href="https://teams.microsoft.com/meet/3594970697800?p=FqJt4Q4BC3pMbScJ8s" target="_blank" id="x_x_meet_invite_block.action.join_link" title="Meeting join" rel="noopener noreferrer"><u>https://teams.microsoft.com/meet/3594970697800?p=FqJt4Q4BC3pMbScJ8s</u></a></span><span>&nbsp\;</span></div>\n<div><span>Num&eacute\;ro de r&eacute\;union :&nbsp\;</span><span>359 497 069 780 0</span><span>&nbsp\;</span></div>\n<div><span>Code secret :&nbsp\;</span><span>Ex3B2xo7</span><span>&nbsp\;</span></div>\n<div><span><a href="https://aka.ms/JoinTeamsMeeting?omkt=fr-BE" target="_blank" id="x_x_meet_invite_block.action.help" rel="noopener noreferrer"><u>Besoin d&apos\;aide ?</u></a></span><span>&nbsp\;</span><span>|</span><span>&nbsp\;</span><span><a href="https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19%3ameeting_YTNjNzY1ZGMtYzI3My00NzE3LThlYjctYTliYTVjMGQ2YzA3%40thread.v2/0?context=%7b%22Tid%22%3a%227ab090d4-fa2e-4ecf-bc7c-4127b4d582ec%22%2c%22Oid%22%3a%223ae5a043-dd2e-4b71-a2c8-e19aabed8100%22%7d" target="_blank" id="x_x_meet_invite_block.action.join_link_compatibility" rel="noopener noreferrer"><u>R&eacute\;f&eacute\;rence syst&egrave\;me</u></a></span></div>\n<div><span>Pour les organisateurs :&nbsp\;</span><span><a href="https://teams.microsoft.com/meetingOptions/?organizerId=3ae5a043-dd2e-4b71-a2c8-e19aabed8100&tenantId=7ab090d4-fa2e-4ecf-bc7c-4127b4d582ec&threadId=19_meeting_YTNjNzY1ZGMtYzI3My00NzE3LThlYjctYTliYTVjMGQ2YzA3@thread.v2&messageId=0&language=fr-BE" target="_blank" id="x_x_meet_invite_block.action.organizer_meet_options" rel="noreferrer noopener"><u>Options de r&eacute\;union</u></a></span></div></body></html>
